body_html: This appears to be due to an incorrect iOS Makefile that attempts to link against version d02e6a705c30 instead of version 5f86b31739cd of the Eigen codebase. This is fixed in pull request 2805.

body: This appears to be due to an incorrect iOS Makefile that attempts to link against version d02e6a705c30 instead of version 5f86b31739cd of the Eigen codebase. This is fixed in [pull request 2805](https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/pull/2805/files).
